snippet: Kelly Olynyk had 21 points and 12 rebounds, and top-ranked Gonzaga routed Saint Mary’s on Monday in the West Coast Conference tournament final.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Gonzaga beats Saint Mary's, 65-51, in West Coast Conference tournament final; other scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Kelly Olynyk had 21 points and 12 rebounds, and top-ranked Gonzaga routed Saint Mary’s on Monday in the West Coast Conference tournament final.
